title: Empty Nest
description:
An empty bird's nest.

May be used to talk about actual nests or birds. May also be used to talk about home in general or to represent phrases like nest egg or empty nest.

apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the empty nest emoji depicts a charming, woven bird's nest, subtly shaded to convey a sense of depth and natural texture. The soft, organic curves of the nest are highlighted with gentle gradients, suggesting a quiet, serene scene. It evokes feelings of transition, independence, or a peaceful absence, often used to represent children leaving home or a sense of quiet solitude, all rendered with Apple's characteristic visual polish.
